meaningMnemonic: When something is <kanji>dense</kanji> to a certain <kanji>degree</kanji>, you’re talking about the <vocabulary>density</vocabulary> or <vocabulary>concentration</vocabulary> of something.
readingMnemonic: This is a jukugo word, which usually means on'yomi readings from the kanji. If you know the readings of your kanji you'll know how to read this as well.
